Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Ideal for owner occupier or investors

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer for sale via Auction, 35 Mary Parade, Rydalmere.

Key property features include:

- 446sqm* site area
- 316sqm* warehouse area
- Access via two (2) roller shutter doors (side access)
- Zoning: IN2 Light Industrial
- Well presented office accommodation
- Car-parking available on-site
- 3 phase power
- Offered with vacant possession
- Full staff amenities


Auction will be held on-site, Wednesday 23rd September at 3.30pm (AEST).

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agents.

*approx.

CBRE as exclusive selling agents, on behalf of our valued client are pleased to present 27 Mary Parade, Rydalmere. 

This property boasts a 300sqm* building area on a 446sqm* parcel of land and is located in close proximity to amenities and the M4 Motorway in the tightly held Rydalmere precinct. 

The IN2: Light Industrial zoning, the internal clearance of up to 5m and on-site parking makes this property very attractive to owner occupiers and investors.

27 Mary Parade, Rydalmere benefits from the following key property features:
- 446sqm* site area
- 300sqm* warehouse area
- Access via one (1) roller shutter door
- Zoning: IN2 Light Industrial
- Well-presented office accommodation
- Car-parking available on-site
- 3 phase power
- 5m* internal clearance
- Offered with vacant possession
- Full staff amenities
- Existing DA for construction of showroom with first floor office

27 Mary Parade, Rydalmere will be sold via on-line auction at 1pm, Wednesday 22nd September.

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*approx

This property is located in an ideal central location close to Silverwater, Parramatta roads and the M4 Motorway. Inside, multiple units are available or together for a larger premises. These units will be sure to go quickly. 

A few key features of this property include:
- Flexible units available ranging from 1,500sqm* to 10,000sqm*
- Large office or small office - you decide!
- High power requirement
- High clearance warehouses
- Older style premises
- Parking and amenities to suit
- IN1 General Industrial location

To find out more, please contact the listed agents.

*=approx
